data.description: You won't want to miss this well maintained 4 bed, 2 bath home features a living room with a gas fireplace and is perfect for entertaining! The kitchen has quartz countertops, a double oven and pantry.  Master bedroom has patio access, a bathroom with a double vanity and his/her closets! Enjoy your outside family time under the covered patio! New paint & carpet 2022. This property has an assumable loan.
